Minor follow-up thing: we might want to consider renaming this Manage menu or finding somewhere more intuitive to put it, now that the page is called Members & Groups. The Manage menu appears on the Members tab and the Groups tab and arguably has little to do with managing either.

Maybe making it a settings icon right next to the organization name to leverage visual closeness or moving it to some other tab (or a new dedicated org info and settings tab)? Itâ€™s not a huge deal but definitely something I noticed when updating the docs for managing preview features.
